data.description: Beautiful well kept spacious 3 bedroom 2.5 bathroom, just walking distance from a city park and less than a 5 minute drive from Expressway 83. A cozy home in a great neighborhood is a dream come true for many people. It's a place where you can feel comfortable while enjoying the benefits of a vibrant community. Stepping inside, you're greeted by a warm and welcoming ambiance. The interior features an open floor plan that seamlessly connects the living room, dining area, office  and kitchen, creating a spacious and inviting atmosphere
